title: 'Music Is Medicine', Tim Booth/James (Short Film)
description:
The music of James contains one of the most complete records of the process of spiritual transformation in music. But until now, the author of these lyrics has not shared where his inspiration came from. In this full and frank conversation with Rebel Wisdom's David Fuller, Tim explains the full backstory for the first time.

This is a short clip from the longer film 'Music & Transformation', watch it here: https://youtu.be/7nQaUL1Ff2k
